Package: lfc
Type: Package
Title: Log Fold Change Distribution Tools for Working with Ratios of Counts
Version: 0.2.2
Author: Florian Erhard
Maintainer: Florian Erhard <florian.erhard@uni-wuerzburg.de>
Description: Ratios of count data such as obtained from RNA-seq are modelled
    using Bayesian statistics to derive posteriors for effects sizes.
